### BDSA
- [C] [BDSA-2020-3372](https://openhub.net/vulnerabilities/bdsa/BDSA-2020-3372) - Xstream Vulnerable to Remote Code Execution (RCE) via Incomplete Blacklist for Unmarshalling Specially Crafted Input
